Description: applet for COSMIC to manage cloud mounts and offline storage mirrors
 Cloud Mounter manages supported cloud and network storage connections from the
 COSMIC panel.
 .
 It can manage online mounts and offline mirrors for OneDrive, Google Drive,
 Box, and SMB through external tools such as rclone, onedriver, and onedrive.
